ps://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00232\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00232-HK</a>)            下跌        4.7%            ;        中航科工(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02357:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02357\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02357-HK</a>)            下跌        3.16%    。</p></section></main>",
